



Anonymous User should be able to view overview of all beds.
test: API endpoint GET /bed
Anonymous User should be able to view details of single bed.
test: API endpoint GET /bed/:bedNumber


Admin should be able to leave note for bed owner.
test: API endpoint POST /bed/:bedNumber/notifications/{message}
Admin should be able to edit owner.


Bed owner should be able to view bed plus notifications.
test: API endpoint GET /bed/:bedNumber/notifications
Bed owner should be able to add/edit details of bed.
test: API endpoint POST /bed/:bedNumber/{updatedData}
Bed owner should be able to edit details of bed positions.
test: API endpoint POST /bed/:bedNumber/:xpos:ypos/{updatedData}
Bed owner should be able to delete notifications.